sequenceDiagram
participant User
participant API
User->>API: Request
alt Success
  API->>User: 200 OK
else Error
  API->>User: 500 Error
end
opt Retry
  User->>API: Retry
end
loop Every minute
  API->>User: Ping
end
par Parallel requests
  User->>API: Request A
and
  User->>API: Request B
end
critical Critical section
  API->>User: Lock acquired
option Timeout
  API->>User: Lock timeout
end
rect rgb(200, 200, 200)
  User->>API: In box
end
break Error occurred
  User->>API: Stop
end
